Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences across all cases
Percentage of variants that contain SW-Awaiting AE Assignment immediately after SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Number of times SW-Awaiting AE Assignment is followed by SW-Initial Reviewer Selection

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences that lead to a reviewer assignment phase (e.g., followed by SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion across the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Percentage of variants where SW-Awaiting AE Assignment appears before any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, or SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in cases that eventually result in SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences that are not followed by any AE assignment activity within 14 days
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all cases

Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment events that occur in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed is eventually observed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment relative to the total number of AE-involved activities (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers, SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases containing SW-Awaiting AE Assignment that proceed to at least one round of review (indicated by presence of SW-Reviewer Agreed or SW-Reviewer Declined)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences to Manuscript Export Succeeded events
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment that appears in variants with performance duration above the median case duration
